Hi, 
how do we download the invoices/transactions?

Hi there! To download your invoices or transactions, you can follow these steps:
1. Log in to your NewsBreak Ad Manager account.
2. Navigate to the 'Billing' section.
3. Here, you will find options to view and download your invoices and transaction history.
If you need more detailed instructions, please refer to this article: [NewsBreak Advertising Cost](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17959734533005-NewsBreak-Advertising-Cost).
Unfortunately there is no option to download anything in the billing section

I'm sorry to hear that you're having trouble finding the download option. It might be a specific issue with your account or a temporary glitch. Please email our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com with details about your issue, and they will assist you further.
